task.summary: Added League, Team, and Player to data model as well as simple UI.
Add save/load functionality and refactor data abstraction to include interfaces/abstract classes.
Integrate abstract class functionality to ui interaction loop.
Implement and test exceptions for matching/not matching list items.
Implement a HashMap to connect teams and their rosters. Remove redundant classes.
Refactor classes to increase cohesion and reduce coupling.
